  "prompt": "What I have to do If I didn't get mail for location selection from congnizant or cognizant pre joining formalities mail?",
  "response": "If you haven't received the location selection or pre-joining formalities email from Cognizant, here are some steps you can take:\n\n1. Check spam/junk folder\n- Look through your spam or junk email folders\n- Sometimes important emails get filtered automatically\n\n2. Verify email address\n- Confirm that the email address you provided during the hiring process is correct\n- Check if there are any typos in your email address\n\n3. Contact Cognizant HR\n- Reach out to the HR representative who conducted your interview\n- Email the campus recruitment team\n- Contact Cognizant's recruitment helpline\n\n4. Alternative communication channels\n- Check your registered phone number for any messages\n- Log in to the Cognizant recruitment portal (if available)\n- Check previous email communication for contact details\n\n5. Follow-up actions\n- Send a polite email explaining your situation\n- Request them to resend the location selection/pre-joining mail\n- Provide your contact details and application/offer letter reference number\n\nRecommended contact methods:\n- Campus_Support@cognizant.com\n- Recruitment helpline\n- LinkedIn connections with Cognizant HR professionals\n\nRemain patient and professional while seeking resolution.",
